This backend implementation provides:
1. OpenShift client configuration
2. Model for deployment status
3. Service to fetch deployment information
4. REST API endpoint
5. CORS configuration for frontend access
6. Basic monitoring endpoints

This implementation provides:
1. Real-time deployment status updates every 30 seconds
2. Environment-based filtering (SIT, UAT, PROD)
3. Visual health indicators
4. Responsive grid layout
5. Error handling and loading states